visual.name: BoxandWhiskerByMAQSoftware
visual.displayName: Box and Whisker by MAQ Software
visual.description: This visual displays data distribution into quartiles in a box with a thin line going through it (whiskers) indicating variability outside the upper and lower quartiles.

flip.description: Changes the orientation of the visual

median.description: How the median is calculated, inclusive or exclusive

boxWidth.description: Manipulate width of boxes and whiskers

boxTransparency.description: Control the transparency of the boxes

whiskerTransparency.description: Control the transparency of the whiskers

meanColor.description: Choose the fill color for mean

decimalPlaces.description: Select the number of decimal places to display

fontSize.description: Font size of Y-Axis micro labels

labelsFontFamily.description: Select the font-family for Y-Axis labels

minWidth.description: Minimum height of each Y-Axis label

titleFontFamily.description: Select the font-family for Y-Axis title

fontSize.description: Font size of Y-Axis micro labels

decimalPlaces.description: Select the number of decimal places to display

minWidth.description: Minimum width of each X-Axis label

titleFontFamily.description: Select the font-family for X-Axis title

showTitle.description: Display a title for legend symbols
